@baseUrl = http://localhost:8003

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Signup
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rajitha@example.com",
  "username": "rajitha",
  "password": "securepass123"
}

### Signup - Second User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "username": "john",
  "password": "securepass456"
}

### Signup - Duplicate Email (should return 409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rajitha@example.com",
  "username": "rajitha2",
  "password": "securepass789"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rajitha@example.com",
  "password": "securepass123"
}

### Login - Wrong Password (should return 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rajitha@example.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### Verify Token (replace with actual token from login response)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify-token?token=REPLACE_WITH_TOKEN

### Get Current User (replace with actual UUID from signup/login response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me?user_id=REPLACE_WITH_UUID